{
  "id": "6a37964862c30505960363d9",
  "title": "身にあまるお話ですが",
  "created": 1782027896,
  "updated": 1782028051,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a37964862c30505960363d9",
      "text": "身にあまるお話ですが",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027896,
      "updated": 1782027896
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37968e000000000061af6b",
      "text": "[https://img.shields.io/badge/😦-身にあまるお話ですが-ccc.svg?style=social#.svg]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027918,
      "updated": 1782027930
    },
    {
      "id": "6a379678000000000061af68",
      "text": "自分の評価以上の過分な期待や称賛を受けた際に、感謝と謙遜を伝える表現",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027896,
      "updated": 1782027897
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37968c000000000061af6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027916,
      "updated": 1782027916
    },
    {
      "id": "6a379700000000000061af72",
      "text": "過分なお言葉をいただき…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782028032,
      "updated": 1782028051
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3796e1000000000061af70",
      "text": "身に余る光栄に存じます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782028001,
      "updated": 1782028029
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3796fc000000000061af71",
      "text": "分不相応なお話をいただき…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782028029,
      "updated": 1782028029
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3796bf000000000061af6f",
      "text": "身に余るご評価をいただき、恐縮の至りです",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027968,
      "updated": 1782027999
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37969c000000000061af6c",
      "text": "もったいないお話で、恐縮です",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027933,
      "updated": 1782027966
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3796be000000000061af6e",
      "text": "私にはもったいなすぎるお言葉です",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1782027966,
      "updated": 1782027966
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3796ba000000000061af6d",
